Author: TheAllMightiest
Text: Hi! I'm sorry your sibling isn't being empathetic/considerate to your eating disorder. I'm proud of you for being brave through the worst of it. Take care of yourself, mentally and physically, and remember that you are not your eating disorder. Try to find joy in your vacation surroundings and set up a self-care plan and support network for yourself when you get back to college.  Love and hugs!
